Comment: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.36,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.70,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直响着的沉默的警铃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是谁的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:27.52,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳进去跳进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.88,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起来 破坏掉这无理的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.47,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不开这沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.89,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.22,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到终幕我都要说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:39.09,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Gear up! 这不是玩笑
Comment: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.95,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Nighty night
Comment: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:42.63,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Oh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:45.15,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}去舍弃掉吧 rulers
Comment: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.98,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Comment: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:48.07,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}One day…
Comment: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:55.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:32.60,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,波打つざわめき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:36.12,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,彩度を失う記憶に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.71,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,願いは幾度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.47,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,数えてみたって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:45.16,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,震えている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:48.94,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,晦冥を揺らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.18,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,希望に似てた歌を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:55.80,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,祈れば砂のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.33,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,零れ落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:03.00,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,ずっと知っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.39,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,密かに息吹く想い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:10.18,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた鋼に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:14.41,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,意味もなく　際限なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:16.32,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,廻るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:21.10,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,世界が引き裂かれても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:24.83,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,結んだ手離さずいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:29.26,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,歪んだ支配が朽ちても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:30.94,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,その名を呼ぶの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:34.97,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,綺麗なアイじゃなくっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:38.92,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,息をするたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:42.98,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,あなた求めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:47.21,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,どこへはぐれてしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:49.45,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:32.60,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,起起落落的杂音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:36.12,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,在失去色彩的记忆中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.71,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,祈求了多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.47,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,只是数一数
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:45.16,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,也混身震颤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:48.94,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,像是那波动黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.18,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,希望似的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:55.80,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,祈祷的话就会像沙砾一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.33,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,凋零飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:03.00,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我一直都知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.39,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,那呼吸中不为人知的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:10.18,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,接触到了生锈的钢铁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:14.41,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,没有意义 没有终点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:16.32,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,循环
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:21.10,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算世界崩裂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:24.83,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我们握紧的手也不会分开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:29.26,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算扭曲的统治腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:30.94,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我也会呼唤那个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:34.97,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算不是美丽的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:38.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我只要一息尚存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:42.98,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,便在寻求着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:47.21,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,无论迷失在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:49.45,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,再一次
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
